            "value": "<p>Sometimes called \"deadly nightshade\", belladonna is a widely available toxin produced from a plant similar to a tomato.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">D</span> Interact (Ingested)</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> <span data-pf2-saving-throw=\"fortitude\" data-pf2-dc=\"19\" data-pf2-traits=\"alchemical,consumable,ingested,poison\" data-pf2-label=\"Belladonna DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Fortitude</span></p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 10 minutes</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 30 minutes</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Dazzled]{Dazzled} (10 minutes)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> <a class=\"inline-roll roll\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\" title=\"1d6\"><i class=\"fas fa-dice-d20\"></i> 1d6</a> poison damage and @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened} 1 (10 minutes)</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> <a class=\"inline-roll roll\" data-mode=\"roll\" data-flavor=\"\" data-formula=\"1d6\" title=\"1d6\"><i class=\"fas fa-dice-d20\"></i> 1d6</a> poison damage, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Confused]{Confused}, and sickened 1 (1 minute)</p>"
